      "content": "thanks. so if i use the higher COGS like you said, the ratio goes up, right? but i'm also seeing reports that the shrinkage is happening mostly at night in the smaller aisles. it's super weird because the security footage just shows nothing happening, but stuff is clearly missing by morning. do u have any ideas on how to track where the loss is coming from more effectively?",
